{"tid":1877873,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港人社區祈福新邨9宗確診","createTime":"2020-02-13T09:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T09:42:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2d5168b65ef5eadf467c0c88e35626a59802e879","tid":1877873,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:13:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200213/H3KMOBA45QUYZRAKI7HQ3U6VQU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200213%2FH3KMOBA45QUYZRAKI7HQ3U6VQU%2F&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebUn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=73f2798d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200213%2FH3KMOBA45QUYZRAKI7HQ3U6VQU%2F&h=eaae2f0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200213/H3KMOBA45QUYZRAKI7HQ3U6VQU/</a><br />\n<br />\n港人社區祈福新邨9宗確診<br />\n<br />\n許多港人居住的番禺祈福新邨至今確診九宗武漢肺炎病例，在當地居住的港人林太表示，邨內暫時未聽聞有港人受感染。官方公佈九宗病例均為輸入病例，是近期從湖北返回或探親的。林太稱，最早一名確診的是湖北大媽，由家鄉回來後曾去按摩店，並到祈福醫院求診，令按摩師和醫生都擔心被感染。她又稱，祈福新邨所有娛樂場所和食店也全面停業，當地港人多躲在家中不出門，未有返回香港。區內祈福醫院日前因有三人確診，被勒令全面停診。院方總機接線生昨對《蘋果》表示，三名確診的病人都是湖北籍的，醫院所有門診都已停診，「因為要全面排查和消毒，最快要20日重開」。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，祈福新邨近日出動大型霧炮車、噴霧機、灑水車等，對樓宇內部及公共區域進行徹底消毒，目擊者稱消毒車輛開過時，一片霧氣蒙蒙，空氣中瀰漫着藥水味，地面上一片濕漉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200213/large/1581525192_75e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200213%2Flarge%2F1581525192_75e6.jpg&h=01c2dc0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n祈福新邨昨出動噴霧車在社區消毒。互聯網"},{"pid":"4cfbd55c9d1b8d2037e6f71dce33ae8be99ad8ee","tid":1877873,"uid":173598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:15:47.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"15fa2b52db94ef6e06ad879b23eb343a19e8dca2","tid":1877873,"uid":320676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:18:14.000Z","msg":"擁抱大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c890ba6ba6d14b6a95b892cb7e39909877bf403e","tid":1877873,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:36:16.000Z","msg":"睇名以為講緊香港<br />\n再睇圖一睇就知係大陸<br />\n陣柒味真係冇得頂"},{"pid":"822360065bdb7ca2684e6d04d698ceb7bd0ded91","tid":1877873,"uid":335002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:42:01.000Z","msg":"成日都睇錯做'折'福新邨"}]}